General
=======
This is a simple shellscript for installing an Openstack Cloud on multible or single node. The installation is guided with dialogs which makes the configuration much easier.

Usage
=====

::
./install.sh
::

If you want to preconfigure all Settings you can copy the preesed.conf.example to preseed.conf and set the variables.
::
cp preseed.conf.example preseed.conf
::
